  <lyrics>[V1]
 /Hermanos, takinachej Diosninchejman
 Kay p’unchaypi sumaj kusiywan./
 
[C]
 /Señor Jesuswanña kaspa
 Tukuyninchej yupaychana./
 
[V2]
 /Hermanos, tukuyninchej kusikuywan
 Yupaychana Señorninchejta./
 
[V3]
 /Hermanos, Dios Tataman gloria kachun
 Kay p'unchaypi wiñaynintímpaj./
 
</lyrics></song>